  "html_size": 197066,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221161524087\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221161524087\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>안녕하세요~</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>오래간만이에요</p><p>그동안 저희 이수한의원이&nbsp;공사기간이라<span>&nbsp;블로그를 못올렸어요</span></p><p><br /></p><p>이게... 이수한의원에서 늘쓰던 컴퓨터가 아니다보니&nbsp;</p><p>다른 컴퓨터를 쓰면 너무 불편하네요 ㅠㅠ</p><p><br /></p><p>하지만 오늘은 특별히</p><p>저희 이수한의원 소식을 알리기 위해 지금 글을 쓰고있지말입니다 ^^</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>저희 이수한의원 식구들 모두 잘 지내고있습니다</p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/line_characters_in_love/original_6.png?type=p50_50\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-6\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>(지금 이 글을 읽고 계신 분도 잘 지내고 계신가요? ^_^&nbsp;)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>일단 제일 먼저 저희 한의원공사는 잘 마무리 되고있습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>아래 사진들은 이수한의원의 모든 물건들을 철거하고&nbsp;</p><p><span>공사&nbsp;첫주에&nbsp;찍은 사진들이에요</span></p><p><span><br /></span></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjM0/MDAxNTEzMDc2MTAwMzc3.wGXUl-d1OBA36algpW3qyOvjahtZ7yGP_1bMf2nH1uAg.pZpDu7c8lrH-ToFrGh7MpkLNUMQsLgxvQq0XZAUd0KQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181901130.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjM0/MDAxNTEzMDc2MTAwMzc3.wGXUl-d1OBA36algpW3qyOvjahtZ7yGP_1bMf2nH1uAg.pZpDu7c8lrH-ToFrGh7MpkLNUMQsLgxvQq0XZAUd0KQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181901130.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjM0/MDAxNTEzMDc2MTAwMzc3.wGXUl-d1OBA36algpW3qyOvjahtZ7yGP_1bMf2nH1uAg.pZpDu7c8lrH-ToFrGh7MpkLNUMQsLgxvQq0XZAUd0KQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181901130.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>밖에서 보는 현관문이에요</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfOSAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5ODk4.KoHMYodSLi_yJ3uv0dc8RA_vb5pArAEVbSHI9BQhR24g.XvboSMHF6zBy6FmBv2kRXi0NR3YyRfXzOa7q0PogApkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181900420.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfOSAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5ODk4.KoHMYodSLi_yJ3uv0dc8RA_vb5pArAEVbSHI9BQhR24g.XvboSMHF6zBy6FmBv2kRXi0NR3YyRfXzOa7q0PogApkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181900420.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfOSAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5ODk4.KoHMYodSLi_yJ3uv0dc8RA_vb5pArAEVbSHI9BQhR24g.XvboSMHF6zBy6FmBv2kRXi0NR3YyRfXzOa7q0PogApkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181900420.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p>원내안쪽에서 보는 현관문이에요</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjg1/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5Nzc5.yF6IhczpHyoXIR5jXyExOciu3Xe4LU_Oc4t-UvzjUk4g.X2NoHiGKVIG5zXnndWxPeJXvqUvsJSYs67wlig0wq6Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181900205.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjg1/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5Nzc5.yF6IhczpHyoXIR5jXyExOciu3Xe4LU_Oc4t-UvzjUk4g.X2NoHiGKVIG5zXnndWxPeJXvqUvsJSYs67wlig0wq6Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181900205.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjg1/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5Nzc5.yF6IhczpHyoXIR5jXyExOciu3Xe4LU_Oc4t-UvzjUk4g.X2NoHiGKVIG5zXnndWxPeJXvqUvsJSYs67wlig0wq6Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181900205.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p>대기실 접수데스크 쪽입니다</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjI0/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5Mjc2.bJSAGPhLlpglEEyBT91M-cv-5NscO0dErgIbTbPYps4g.Tykie0zEN3z6MQ-asMGjnaEmE_iwnYMZByo5DMsAe5og.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859402.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjI0/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5Mjc2.bJSAGPhLlpglEEyBT91M-cv-5NscO0dErgIbTbPYps4g.Tykie0zEN3z6MQ-asMGjnaEmE_iwnYMZByo5DMsAe5og.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859402.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjI0/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5Mjc2.bJSAGPhLlpglEEyBT91M-cv-5NscO0dErgIbTbPYps4g.Tykie0zEN3z6MQ-asMGjnaEmE_iwnYMZByo5DMsAe5og.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859402.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p>치료실이구요</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfNiAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk4OTcz.7EeLX_o1yBzy3e_o8JyTcUeyxhRIyn8riHF8qpAQlHUg.FwEmRG21lIoDABzw3300fMuun4L7qPvvAbALDIB471Mg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859194.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfNiAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk4OTcz.7EeLX_o1yBzy3e_o8JyTcUeyxhRIyn8riHF8qpAQlHUg.FwEmRG21lIoDABzw3300fMuun4L7qPvvAbALDIB471Mg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859194.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfNiAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk4OTcz.7EeLX_o1yBzy3e_o8JyTcUeyxhRIyn8riHF8qpAQlHUg.FwEmRG21lIoDABzw3300fMuun4L7qPvvAbALDIB471Mg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859194.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p>탈의실 입니다</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfNTQg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5NjM4.k5K-5GSkif18WEBSL6CWjvhueD5WdzX35jYcwUwSeyIg.kwiQiE9XyWrRzE0AsA4GfpNCYEatrHSkVmLdKO7HhTsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859989.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfNTQg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5NjM4.k5K-5GSkif18WEBSL6CWjvhueD5WdzX35jYcwUwSeyIg.kwiQiE9XyWrRzE0AsA4GfpNCYEatrHSkVmLdKO7HhTsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859989.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfNTQg/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5NjM4.k5K-5GSkif18WEBSL6CWjvhueD5WdzX35jYcwUwSeyIg.kwiQiE9XyWrRzE0AsA4GfpNCYEatrHSkVmLdKO7HhTsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859989.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p>여기는 조제실</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTY3/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5NDQ2.EPqsOpkHhoBVQSCRR1iqAFnVKhO9TdlRkXQkaczvS2Yg.w3LT4CYmIUTEq_nOjw06vkEKf74FqlYs5vxv_ULeT5Yg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859746.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTY3/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5NDQ2.EPqsOpkHhoBVQSCRR1iqAFnVKhO9TdlRkXQkaczvS2Yg.w3LT4CYmIUTEq_nOjw06vkEKf74FqlYs5vxv_ULeT5Yg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859746.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTY3/MDAxNTEzMDc2MDk5NDQ2.EPqsOpkHhoBVQSCRR1iqAFnVKhO9TdlRkXQkaczvS2Yg.w3LT4CYmIUTEq_nOjw06vkEKf74FqlYs5vxv_ULeT5Yg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181859746.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>마지막으로&nbsp;탕전실이에요</p><p><br /></p><p>아직 공사가 다 끝나려면 한참 있어야해서... 지저분하네요 ㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그리고 2주가 지난 오늘 또 찍었습니다<span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>놀라지마세요&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>따라라~</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTcg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2Mjg2.qv8WtwgJn9dTiJDoIlcTH4BUpgVPeUCG4Q5VsYjNonsg.eVN5FeyDHmitcRZhRJrg56uTPTxk7kwp9TwrH_Fn47Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805647.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTcg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2Mjg2.qv8WtwgJn9dTiJDoIlcTH4BUpgVPeUCG4Q5VsYjNonsg.eVN5FeyDHmitcRZhRJrg56uTPTxk7kwp9TwrH_Fn47Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805647.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTcg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2Mjg2.qv8WtwgJn9dTiJDoIlcTH4BUpgVPeUCG4Q5VsYjNonsg.eVN5FeyDHmitcRZhRJrg56uTPTxk7kwp9TwrH_Fn47Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805647.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>원내에서 보는 현관문입니다</p><p>기존에 문은 손잡이식 불투명&nbsp;유리 문이었는데</p><p>이제는 슬라이드식 투명&nbsp;유리문입니다</p><p><br /></p><p>더이상 손잡이로 잡아당기지안고&nbsp;\"눌러주세요\" 버트을&nbsp;누르시면</p><p>문이 옆으로 쓱~ 열릴거에요&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>기대되시죠? ^^&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjUz/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2MTI3.3TTvVIrcyYqtNg9OVCPFtB70Rur0pzO1XCmBlqD87HQg.dS8QcqYj8PhBfl82AcE_6_RbaG654CtOmK27lxNgV4Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805392.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjUz/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2MTI3.3TTvVIrcyYqtNg9OVCPFtB70Rur0pzO1XCmBlqD87HQg.dS8QcqYj8PhBfl82AcE_6_RbaG654CtOmK27lxNgV4Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805392.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjUz/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2MTI3.3TTvVIrcyYqtNg9OVCPFtB70Rur0pzO1XCmBlqD87HQg.dS8QcqYj8PhBfl82AcE_6_RbaG654CtOmK27lxNgV4Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805392.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>이건 이수한의원 신발장&nbsp;</p><p>내원 하시는 환자분들 신발은 여기에 보관하시고</p><p>원내 슬리퍼로 갈아주시면 됩니다</p><p><br /></p><p>얼른 슬리퍼로 채우고싶어요<br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfOTcg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2NDM3.-cCA2T0PlZKWlMNm0Ft9Qq9Mv9qyTrNMSVF0Ec5VG7gg.JipUzlmTeKzgg30WPyC8wWcCKGh2GIITK2hPYRsDwmIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805897.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfOTcg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2NDM3.-cCA2T0PlZKWlMNm0Ft9Qq9Mv9qyTrNMSVF0Ec5VG7gg.JipUzlmTeKzgg30WPyC8wWcCKGh2GIITK2hPYRsDwmIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805897.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfOTcg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2NDM3.-cCA2T0PlZKWlMNm0Ft9Qq9Mv9qyTrNMSVF0Ec5VG7gg.JipUzlmTeKzgg30WPyC8wWcCKGh2GIITK2hPYRsDwmIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805897.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>여긴 모든 환자분들이 꼭 오셔야하는 데스크입니다</p><p>아직 미완성이에요</p><p><br /></p><p>기존에있던 데스크보다는 깔끔하니 이쁠거같죠?&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjMg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2NjIz.cjKtUdR1O-PENFKQsd18bfFZdwNgy4XkXHmR46ph888g.46HooTmz_rE0F5q2ono7HSoSJaI5VpgOrHqqwdk-fD8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806980.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjMg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2NjIz.cjKtUdR1O-PENFKQsd18bfFZdwNgy4XkXHmR46ph888g.46HooTmz_rE0F5q2ono7HSoSJaI5VpgOrHqqwdk-fD8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806980.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjMg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2NjIz.cjKtUdR1O-PENFKQsd18bfFZdwNgy4XkXHmR46ph888g.46HooTmz_rE0F5q2ono7HSoSJaI5VpgOrHqqwdk-fD8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806980.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>여기는 대기실에요</p><p>여기 보이는 장은.. 책장입니다.</p><p>그 위에 티비가 올라갈거구요</p><p><br /></p><p>왼쪽과 오른쪽으로 보이는 문은 진료실이구요</p><p><br /></p><p>이제 원장님이 두분이시니 진료실도 두개!&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTEx/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2OTAw.-SetKzFf6rpIhJGQnGUX2dRm-mhuBLFuOkX-h-GEjqUg.lAa9PlE8-kZ8rzzHA_Urpwv7aV8UB5EU3DczMuoNG8wg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806727.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTEx/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2OTAw.-SetKzFf6rpIhJGQnGUX2dRm-mhuBLFuOkX-h-GEjqUg.lAa9PlE8-kZ8rzzHA_Urpwv7aV8UB5EU3DczMuoNG8wg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806727.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTEx/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY2OTAw.-SetKzFf6rpIhJGQnGUX2dRm-mhuBLFuOkX-h-GEjqUg.lAa9PlE8-kZ8rzzHA_Urpwv7aV8UB5EU3DczMuoNG8wg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806727.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjM0/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3MTAz.Rtpc3waw2kyKjVy7w8K6-HKbm0cJBshcSPoTiszVM_8g.ywvOMxmKW5w5RYHUXBjvJY8FYus6JyycTkshJSvsQIMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805119.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjM0/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3MTAz.Rtpc3waw2kyKjVy7w8K6-HKbm0cJBshcSPoTiszVM_8g.ywvOMxmKW5w5RYHUXBjvJY8FYus6JyycTkshJSvsQIMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805119.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjM0/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3MTAz.Rtpc3waw2kyKjVy7w8K6-HKbm0cJBshcSPoTiszVM_8g.ywvOMxmKW5w5RYHUXBjvJY8FYus6JyycTkshJSvsQIMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181805119.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>원장님들 방은 아직 텅 비었어요<br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfODAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3MzA1.XA-DRrBno7J58fSWz90QXBtQkb_GhQ6c34HI_ABLZpcg.gcbZeTyI9mWdAUv4zdlnstU6yMFgwzh7g3Ga2x3dze4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806190.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfODAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3MzA1.XA-DRrBno7J58fSWz90QXBtQkb_GhQ6c34HI_ABLZpcg.gcbZeTyI9mWdAUv4zdlnstU6yMFgwzh7g3Ga2x3dze4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806190.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfODAg/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3MzA1.XA-DRrBno7J58fSWz90QXBtQkb_GhQ6c34HI_ABLZpcg.gcbZeTyI9mWdAUv4zdlnstU6yMFgwzh7g3Ga2x3dze4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806190.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>여기는 치료실입니다</p><p>아직 가구가 안들어와서 아무것도 없네요</p><p>커텐도 더러워지면 안되니까 비닐로 포장상태구요<br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTY5/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3NDYx.--L_SgnwjOtqxBcmKaHOvmRCNjlAW_wI2Sc_7I1_eR8g.qnHBPZUYkzk9JaMhqBUeOlLlCVG92eukJhL13M2-dzsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806460.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTY5/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3NDYx.--L_SgnwjOtqxBcmKaHOvmRCNjlAW_wI2Sc_7I1_eR8g.qnHBPZUYkzk9JaMhqBUeOlLlCVG92eukJhL13M2-dzsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806460.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E410B77')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMTY5/MDAxNTEzMDc2NTY3NDYx.--L_SgnwjOtqxBcmKaHOvmRCNjlAW_wI2Sc_7I1_eR8g.qnHBPZUYkzk9JaMhqBUeOlLlCVG92eukJhL13M2-dzsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181806460.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p>에이컨도 새로 달았어요</p><p>에어컨과 히터도 모두 되는 신형입니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>공사는 이번주까지만 하면 다끝날거고</p><p>이제 <u><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u>다음주 월요일 12월18일</u></span></b></u>에 새로운모습으로 오픈합니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>보고싶어도 몇일만 더 참고</p><p>다음주 월요일에 봬요 ^^<br style=\"clear:both;\" />&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
